page.title: 11 HOUSING ON WOOSEHILL
page.content: Woosehill is an expanding housing development built on agricultural land .Once the land was released for housing,groups of developers bought sites,capitalising on the many advantages of the location and its easy access to direct routes to London for commuters. There is a lot of variety in both size and style of housing.This ranges from small flats and terraced houses, designed as starter homes for the newly married or single,to large,five_ bedroomed,family homes.Architectural styles vary considerably. The development is served by a spine road,a large supermarket,a community centre and a primary school.Older children attend secondary schools in Wokingham and district.
